author: GameSpot
description:
Fortnite OG returns December 6 2024.

Go all the way back to day one of Season 1 for the classic Fortnite experience! Relive the origins of Fortnite Battle Royale, complete with OG loot, OG locations, and OG gameplay in Fortnite OG Chapter 1 - Season 1!
title: Fortnite OG: Chapter 1 - Season 1 Cinematic Teaser

author: GameSpot
description:
Citadelle des Morts awaits 🏰

This abandoned medieval village and castle hides incredible power—and incredible danger. Survive the horde and overcome new horrors looking to claim their newest victims on December 5 in Season 01 Reloaded 🧟
title: Black Ops 6 Zombies - Citadelle des Morts Gameplay Trailer

author: GameSpot
description:
🕷️Natasha Romanoff is fully prepared - even if the world is on the brink of disaster. Trained in the infamous Red Room to anticipate anything, the Black Widow is always ready for action! For years, she put her unrivaled combat skills to use as a member of the Avengers, keeping pace with some of the most powerful beings who ever lived.

Imbued with a life-extending formula and having outlasted most of her enemies and allies, she continues her battle decades into the future. Her goal? Lead the Red Room in its relentless campaign to overthrow the oppressive reign of Doom 2099.  Sharpen your reflexes and join Black Widow's resistance in Marvel Rivals on December 6th! 

#MarvelRivals #Marvel #MarvelGames #BlackWidow
title: Marvel Rivals - Black Widow Character Gameplay Reveal Trailer | "Super-Spy Sniper"
